popup_text = "\"Octomancy, or the magic of eights, is one of the oldest and simplest magics practiced in Archeopolis. It simply declares that eight of anything and everything is significant, and the more eight-aligned the number, the more powerful it becomes. Any practitioner will quickly realize that doing everything eight times has both a joy and frustration all it's own...\""
